rows.label: tev055101_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev055101_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Wanana about the animals in the caravan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev055101_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Wanana if she's heard any interesting rumors.

rows.label: tev055101_SEL0051
rows.name: Ask Wanana about the battle with the Zu Pharg.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Wanana about Nopon commerce.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_SEL2041
rows.name: Ask Wanana about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG0001
rows.name:
These are special potamuses tamed by Nopon!
We call them nopopotamuses.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG0002
rows.name:
They carry tons of cargo, and Nopon can hide inside
mouth to escape danger while traveling.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG0003
rows.name:
Friend must be crazed with jealousy, mmmm?
Wanana can see it written on friend's face...
Friend wants ride in nopopotamus mouth![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG0004
rows.name:
True, it get kind of slimy in there,
but otherwise quite warm and comfortable.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG017
rows.name:
Nalu from Drongo Caravan getting picked on big time
by nasty Ganglion![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG018
rows.name: Nalu like damsel in distress or something.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG019
rows.name:
Unfortunately, poor Wanana not strong enough to help.
But friend could probably save her in moment![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG020
rows.name:
Drongo Caravan way north in Ouchy Hot Lava Land.
Friend should help out if ever passing by.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG025
rows.name:
Nopopotamuses still scared of big nasty thing.
They nopo-terrified![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG026
rows.name:
They even stopped eating and sleeping at night.
Ganglion all deserve swift kick in butts for this![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG027
rows.name:
Meh! If human friends not take care of it first,
Wanana would have punched Zu Pharg's lights out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG1001
rows.name:
Mira very dangerous. But this work out well for Nopon,
because we charge extra for delivering wares in
danger places.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG1002
rows.name:
Kuta is Nopon merchant legend! Has been everywhere
from Ouchy Hot Lava Land to southern wilderness.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG1003
rows.name:
No Nopon sells more wares or earns bigger money
than Kuta.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG1004
rows.name: Kuta probably making killer sale right this second![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG2001
rows.name:
Wanana recently became pen pal with Nalu from
Drongo Caravan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG2002
rows.name:
It sounds like Nalu is having really tough time.
Nalu got attacked by Ganglion AND terrible indigens!
As if Ouchy Hot Lava Land not bad enough...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG2003
rows.name:
But when Wanana feel bad for Nalu and start to send
care packages, guess what happen?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055101_MSG2004
rows.name:
Nalu write back and say she love Wanana!
Wanana so happy. Might even have to charge Nalu
less for care packages in future...[ST:wait ]
